<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Name"> Name  </span></h5>
<p>Design Walkthrough
</p><p><br />
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="What_is_its_central_functionality"> What is its central functionality </span></h5>
<p>Gather stakehlders or peers
issue a design doc
talk through the documentatins and answer questions/take suggestions for change
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="What_does_it_help_me_do.3F"> What does it help me do? </span></h5>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="What_problem_can_it_help_me_solve.3F"> What problem can it help me solve? </span></h5>
<p>Spot design problems
get buy-in to a design
get understanding of the design by stakeholder and by me
can get stakeholders to discuss/agree between themselves
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Why_would_the_world_be_worse_if_I_didn.27t_use_it.3F"> Why would the world be worse if I didn't use it? </span></h5>
<p>If I just issue docs
a) people don't read them/understand them
b) feedback v. piecemeal
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Why_does_it_help_solve_the_problem.3F"> Why does it help solve the problem? </span></h5>
<p>Talking is a medium people find easier to absorb
People can ask questions and get them resolved quickly
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="In_which_context_is_this_tool_useful.3F">  In which context is this tool useful? </span></h5>
<p>Talking through with 
a) peers
b) the users of the design
c) the implementors of the design
</p><p><br />
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Who_could_benefit_from_using_this_tool.3F"> Who could benefit from using this tool? </span></h5>
<p>Designers/Architects
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="What_are_the_downsides_of_using_this_tool.3F"> What are the downsides of using this tool? </span></h5>
<p>Takes time and organisation
need to take good notes of the meeting
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Are_there_dangers_or_risks_involved.3F"> Are there dangers or risks involved? </span></h5>
<p>If there are obvious flaws you look stupid
Can make snap decision on design changes that may not be good
</p>
<h5> <span class="mw-headline" id="Do_I_need_to_use_other_tools_in_order_to_get_the_full_benefit_from_this_tool.3F"> Do I need to use other tools in order to get the full benefit from this tool? </span></h5>
<p>Need to get written sign-off afterwards
</p><p>Back to <a href="index.php?title=InterpersonalTools" title="InterpersonalTools">InterpersonalTools</a>
</p>
